cards.originalText:
When Soulblade enters the battlefield, exile target creature card with mana value 3 or less from your graveyard.
Whenever equipped creature attacks, create a token that's a copy of a card exiled with Soulblade that's tapped and attacking. Exile the token at end of combat.
Equip {1}

